      "content": "i dont even know why i bother waking up anymore. everything i worked for for the last 5 years... the lab results, the funding, the whole phd... it just feels like it's all gone. i'm just so incredibly tired of fighting. like, there is no point in trying to fix it when the whole foundation is just broken. i just want everything to stop.",
